      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELUSIVE CURL (1) has been in the placings at her last two runs, most recently when third (29.78) in a Grade 5 over 515m at this track. Key player on best and worth another chance. IAN ALBERT (6) produced a fast 29.58 winning over 515m at this track last start in a Grade 5. Expecting another bold showing. ASTON BUGSY (8) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (29.63) at this track behind Keep Rolling in a Grade 5. Led around the bend before fighting on well and should give a sight. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from five starts. Expected to be in this for a long way. MEPUNGA SUMMIT (7) gave nothing else a chance most recently. That form reads well.",
